<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> maturāntakap po
<lb n="2"/>ttappi coḻaṉ Ōlai kaṭṭaṉū
<lb n="3"/>r Ūravar kaṇṭu tiruviṭai taṅka
<lb n="4"/>ḷur Iṟaiyili tevatā
<lb n="5"/>ṉam paḻavakaram
<lb n="6"/>puttakaram nik
<lb n="7"/>ki muppatāvatu Aippaci māta
<lb n="8"/>mutal tiruppukkuḻi vicaiya
<lb n="9"/>rākavap perumāḷukku
</p>

